// Tower Of Hanoi Print Moves 3 (#1456)

// No input. Prints all 7 moves for the 3-disk Tower of Hanoi (from peg `A` to peg `C` using `B`), one per line, formatted `<disk>: <src>-><dst>\n`. Example first move: `1: A->C\n`.

main

def main {
    stl.startup
    stl.output "1: A->C\n2: A->B\n1: C->B\n3: A->C\n1: B->A\n2: B->C\n1: A->C\n"
    stl.loop
}
